As fast food goes, it’s good.   Burgers are juicy & big.  I like their Reuben & sweet potato fries.    And of course... there’s tasty frozen custard.  They even have steamed broccoli, which I appreciate. If you’re driving thru, expect a wait.  They have a system to keep things in order & the wait means your food will be piping hot.  Fries will be fresh & crispy.  Lettuce will crunch.  It’s worth it to us.  It’s still fast food, but not as fast as McD’s.  We don’t mind.
